longBusinessSummary: HK eBus Corporation does not have significant operations. The company intends to seek, investigate, and engage in a business combination with a private entity. Previously, it was engaged in the exploration of oil and gas. The company was formerly known as Rambo Medical Group, Inc. and changed its name to HK eBus Corporation in August 2015. HK eBus Corporation was founded in 2005 and is based in Pasadena, California.
